para_trans: Government Decision No: Narrow-2024 / Q. No.109 / Q.1417
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Read: Department of Planning, Government Decisions, Narrow-2024 / Q.109 / Q.1417,
Department of Planning, Government Decision No: Narrow-2024 / Q.109 / Q.1417 dated 17th March, 2025
Under this, the Maharashtra State Aadhaar Material Policy (Data) 2024 has been announced. The Government's decision
Narrow - 2024 / Q. No. 109 / Q. 1417, dated 17th March, 2025 is being cancelled by order.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
